joiMWllZnkifQ.sG3OqnkHDNZpplC0eLA9u0NYhAE4J8yHwSPDyeVA8k8\" style=\"color: rgb(119,119,119);text-decoration: underline;\">The Cosmopolitan Globalist</a> cross-posted a post from <a href=\"https://substack.com/redirect/82283f75-154c-40b5-9f64-33fad2cdfce3?j=eyJ1IjoiMWllZnkifQ.sG3OqnkHDNZpplC0eLA9u0NYhAE4J8yHwSPDyeVA8k8\" style=\"color: rgb(119,119,119);text-decoration: underline;\">Nervana Mahmoud</a></span></td></tr></tbody></table></td></tr><tr height=\"18\"><td></td></tr><tr><td><table role=\"presentation\" width=\"auto\" border=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\"><tbody><tr><td style=\"vertical-align:middle;\"><img class=\"custom-css-email-avatar avatar-QIQ5yR\" src=\"https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/$s_!dIbD!,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F23e99113-9283-4b3f-be0b-262c220269f4_500x500.jpeg\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box;max-width: 550px;border: none;vertical-align: middle;width: 40px;height: 40px;min-width: 40px;min-height: 40px;object-fit: cover;margin: 0px;display: inline;border-radius: 50%\" width=\"40\" height=\"40\"></td><td width=\"12\" style=\"min-width:12px;\"></td><td style=\"vertical-align:middle;\"><div class=\"email-text-base restacker-name\" style=\"font-family: system-ui,-apple-system,BlinkMacSystemFont,'Segoe UI',Roboto,Helvetica,Arial,sans-serif,'Apple Color Emoji','Segoe UI Emoji','Segoe UI Symbol';color: #363737;font-size: 16px;line-height: 26px;\"><span style=\"display: block;font-weight: 600;\">Claire Berlinski</span><span class=\"email-text-b4\" style=\"font-size: 14px;line-height: 20px;letter-spacing: -.15px;display: block;color: rgb(119,119,119);\">Apr 27 &#183; The Cosmopolitan Globalist</span></div></td></tr></tbody></table></td></tr><tr height=\"18\"><td></td></tr><tr><td><p class=\"email-text-base email-text-b3 intro-text\" style=\"margin: 0 0 20px 0;color: #363737;font-family: system-ui,-apple-system,BlinkMacSystemFont,'Segoe UI',Roboto,Helvetica,Arial,sans-serif,'Apple Color Emoji','Segoe UI Emoji','Segoe UI Symbol';font-size: 16px;line-height: 22px;letter-spacing: -0.45px;margin-top: 0;\"><span>This is an important story. Malians are terrified. It has major implications for global security. It's front-page news in France, with the prominence and analysis a major international story like this deserves. The New York Times and the Washington Post both ran articles about it, but you'd hard-pressed to find the reports on their websites: It's given no prominence at all, suggesting to readers that it's wildly obscure, rather than evidence that more than 20 years after 911, al-Qaeda has not only survived, but adapted and expanded its operations. In the US, you'd think the only thing that happened over the weekend was the fracas at the Hilton. Imagine what our front pages would look like if all those journalists were out in the world, where they belong, in places like Mali? </span></p></td></tr></tbody></table></div><div class=\"post typography\" dir=\"auto\" style=\"--image-offset-margin: -120px;padding: 32px 0 0 0;font-size: 16px;line-height: 26px;\"><div class=\"post-header\" role=\"region\" aria-label=\"Post header\" style=\"font-size: 16px;line-height: 26px;\"><h1 class=\"post-title published title-X77sOw\" dir=\"auto\" style=\"direction: auto;text-align: start;unicode-bidi: isolate;color: rgb(54,55,55);font-family: 'Roboto Slab',sans-serif;font-weight: 700;-webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;-moz-osx-font-smoothing: antialiased;-webkit-appearance: optimizelegibility;-moz-appearance: optimizelegibility;appearance: optimizelegibility;margin: 0;line-height: 36px;font-size: 32px;\"><a href=\"https://substack.com/app-link/post?publication_id=6467213&post_id=195472754&utm_source=cross-post&utm_campaign=16235&isFreemail=false&r=1iefy&token=eyJ1c2VyX2lkIjoyNTM4MTQyLCJwb3N0X2lkIjoxOTU0NzI3NTQsImlhdCI6MTc3NzI4MjM2MCwiZXhwIjoxNzc5ODc0MzYwLCJpc3MiOiJwdWItNjQ2NzIxMyIsInN1YiI6InBvc3QtcmVhY3Rpb24ifQ.E81rcQdkzwSngiW1ZSral3P8agUf_hoKXvMq3FSf1tE\" style=\"color: rgb(54,55,55);text-decoration: none;\">Mali at the Brink: How Strategic Realignment Accelerated Al- Qaeda Insurgency </a></h1><table class=\"post-meta\" role=\"presentation\" width=\"100%\" border=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" style=\"margin: 1em 0;height: 20px;align-items: center;\"><tbody><tr><td><table role=\"presentation\" width=\"auto\" border=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\"><tbody><tr><td><table role=\"presentation\" width=\"auto\" border=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\"><tbody><tr><td style=\"vertical-align:middle;\"><div class=\"pencraft pc-reset color-primary-zABazT line-height-20-t4M0El font-meta-MWBumP size-11-NuY2Zx weight-medium-fw81nC transform-uppercase-yKDgcq reset-IxiVJZ meta-EgzBVA custom-css-email-post-author\" style=\"list-style: none;font-size: 11px;line-height: 20px;text-decoration: unset;color: rgb(54,55,55);margin: 0;font-family: 'SF Compact',-apple-system,system-ui,-apple-system,BlinkMacSystemFont,'Segoe UI',Roboto,Helvetica,Arial,sans-serif,'Apple Color Emoji','Segoe UI Emoji','Segoe UI Symbol';font-weight: 500;text-transform: uppercase;letter-spacing: .2px;\"><a class=\"pencraft pc-reset color-primary-zABazT line-height-20-t4M0El font-meta-MWBumP size-11-NuY2Zx weight-medium-fw81nC transform-uppercase-yKDgcq reset-IxiVJZ meta-EgzBVA\" style=\"list-style: none;color: rgb(54,55,55);margin: 0;font-size: 11px;line-height: 20px;font-family: 'SF Compact',-apple-system,system-ui,-apple-system,BlinkMacSystemFont,'Segoe UI',Roboto,Helvetica,Arial,sans-serif,'Apple Color Emoji','Segoe UI Emoji','Segoe UI Symbol';font-weight: 500;text-transform: uppercase;letter-spacing: .2px;text-decoration: none\" href=\"https://substack.com/@nervana3\">Nervana Mahmoud</a></div></td></tr></tbody></table></td></tr><tr><td><table role=\"presentation\" width=\"auto\" border=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\"><tbody><tr><td style=\"vertical-align:middle;\"><div class=\"pencraft pc-reset color-s